reviewText: This was one of her funniest and informative videos that I have seen. I watched it with all of my friends and we could not stop laughing...and learning. If you are looking to understand the importance of humor in your life to help with stress, than Loretta LaRoche is the person for you! I highly recommend this DVD.
I bought this for my mom.  She was dissappointed with it.. She said the previous dvds were much better... very pricey for the few laughs
